{"tid":1884353,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"董瑤瓊第二：金燕挑戰習近平","createTime":"2020-02-17T14:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T14:10:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b4df237be34aa21aa2182313f87994564c21da","tid":1884353,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:07:10.000Z","msg":"董瑤瓊第二：金燕挑戰習近平<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v7lQWIz9YsY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv7lQWIz9YsY&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=e863d34a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v7lQWIz9YsY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRFA 自由亞洲粵語<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近日，一條中國網民「金燕」在網上挑戰習近平的視頻在網絡瘋傳。有網民稱這名「董瑤瓊第二」金燕剛被公安約談過。在中國新冠肺炎疫情蔓延之際，「金燕」又在網上直接評論習近平「害了全中國」。(視頻來源：楊占青推特)"},{"pid":"6bbe4726fbc44c2e5cb30462bb12e23649c59e47","tid":1884353,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"係咪謝金燕？<br />\n我今夜共你吻過"},{"pid":"b1cdff9b9455c677384e86ccf4a1c40cc9b3f599","tid":1884353,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:10:58.000Z","msg":"一係被消失 一係變精神病出番黎"}]}